{"tid":426037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際廢除核武運動獲諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2017-10-06T09:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T11:35:15.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9524246eea4b753edde96cd7051401a0876bd4","tid":426037,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"國際廢除核武運動獲諾貝爾和平獎<br />\n2017-10-06 HKT 17:04<br />\n<br />\n今屆諾貝爾和平獎，由非政府組織「國際廢除核武運動」奪得。<br />\n<br />\n秘書處設於日內瓦的「國際廢除核武運動」過去十年來，致力令核武成為歷史，亦是上月在聯合國，獲超過40個國家，簽署的禁用核武協議重要倡導者。<br />\n<br />\n協議提出，禁止在任何情況下，發展、測試、製造、持有或存放核子武器。聯合國秘書長古特雷斯認為，協議是重要一步，讓各國達到世界無核武的目標。"},{"pid":"6b3d17dc02f3088068b6abb47c93a7080696aecf","tid":426037,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"諗起GI Joe2假美國總統同其他國家開會個幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a5cc11ffa1bbade91e6b0a41335219853fdabe","tid":426037,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"金仔：無我就無諾貝爾和平獎"},{"pid":"6aec60478f2a218b9a63c52049c2df9a90280795","tid":426037,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔：無我就無諾貝爾和平獎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e992cd7e6cdc61eee4b6f8b67317ce398e1c5dd","tid":426037,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"同上次歐盟拎獎一樣, 九唔搭八"},{"pid":"9203e8064afe434d6a70e36645b664b4de7c4845","tid":426037,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"幾時到廢老？"},{"pid":"db18cf1985236a86213976d3a2816dd43d81b081","tid":426037,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"支美俄北泡四國唔簽，其餘所有國家簽哂都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}